      <title>由于信心持续低迷，中国 8 月份信贷增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-s-credit-growth-slowed-in-august-as-confidence-stays-weak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济前景黯淡，消费者和企业信心低迷，中国8月份信贷扩张速度较上年同期有所放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-s-credit-growth-slowed-in-august-as-confidence-stays-weak</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 11:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
