      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/retail-crowd-piles-into-cme-s-micro-gold-contract-as-metal-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在黄金价格再创纪录之际，散户投资者纷纷涌入芝加哥商品交易所集团（CME Group Inc.）的微型黄金期货合约。]]></description>
